steps.html_instructions: Head north on Atatürk Blv. toward Kurtul Sk.
Make a U-turn at Kurtul Sk.
Continue onto Ertuğrul Gazi Cd.
Continue onto Bilecik Eskişehir Yolu
Continue straight to stay on Bilecik Eskişehir Yolu

Keep right at the fork and merge onto Adapazarı Bilecik Yolu/D650
Continue to follow D650
Keep left to continue on Bilecik Eskişehir Yolu
Keep left at the fork and merge onto Bursa Eskişehir Yolu/D200/E90

Continue onto Bursa Eskişehir Yolu/D200/E90
Continue to follow D200/E90

Merge onto Ankara Çevre Yolu/O-20/E90 via the ramp to Gölbaşı/Konya/Samsun
Continue to follow Ankara Çevre Yolu/O-20
Take the exit toward Şehir Merkezi/Kırıkkale/Samsun/E88/D200
Continue onto Ankara Çevre Yolu Samsun Yolu Bağlantısı

Keep right at the fork, follow signs for Kırıkkale/Kayseri/Samsun and merge onto 19 Mayıs Blv./D200/E88
Continue to follow D200/E88
Continue straight onto Kırıkkale Çorum Yozgat Yolu
Continue onto Kırıkkale Çorum Yolu/D190
Take the ramp to Kırıkkale Tokat Yolu/D190
Continue onto Kırıkkale Tokat Yolu/D190

Turn left to stay on Kırıkkale Tokat Yolu/D190
Continue to follow D190
Turn right onto Zile Cd.
Continue onto Pazar Zile Yolu
Turn left toward Pazar Zile Yolu
Continue onto Pazar Zile Yolu
Continue onto Tokat Pazar Yolu
Continue straight

Slight right onto Tokat Amasya Yolu/D180
Continue to follow D180

Turn right onto Çeçenistan Cd.
Go through 2 roundabouts
At the roundabout, take the 3rd exit and stay on Çeçenistan Cd.

Enter the roundabout
Destination will be on the left
